<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> _:genid2 .
_:genid2 <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/name> "Jiayun Liu"@en .
_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Person> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "DAIMO is an integration profile that connects DCAT-AP, MLDCAT-AP, ODRL, PROV-O, and the Dataspace Protocol (DSP, as operationalised by Eclipse EDC) to support publication, discovery, invocation, execution traceability, and contextualised evaluation of AI model assets exchanged in dataspaces. The edc: namespace is used only for EDC-specific extensions (e.g., ParticipantContext) not yet standardised in DSP."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2026-04-22"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-07-06"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://w3id.org/pionera> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "DAIMO: an ontology for governed AI model assets in dataspaces"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespacePrefix> "daimo" .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespaceUri> "https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#" .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "See the companion documents ONTOLOGY-REFERENCE.md (class-by-class reference), VALIDATION-MATRIX.md (traceability), and daimo-ontology-design.md (design rationale) in the source repository."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo/align> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo/docs> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo/shapes> .
