<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#authorizedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#authorizesRun> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#authorizedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#authorizedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://data.europa.eu/it6/Run> .
<http://data.europa.eu/it6/Run> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#authorizedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#ExecutionAuthorization> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#authorizedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of daimo:authorizesRun. Functional: each run is authorized by exactly one agreement."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#authorizedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "authorized by"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#authorizesRun
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#authorizesRun> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#authorizesRun> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#authorizesRun> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#ExecutionAuthorization> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#authorizesRun> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://data.europa.eu/it6/Run> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#authorizesRun> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an authorization to a run it permits. Non-functional: a single authorization can cover multiple runs (e.g., subscription-style access). Asymmetric: an authorization is distinct from any run it authorises. Deliberately NOT declared a subproperty of prov:used: an odrl:Agreement is a policy artefact (an Entity), not a prov:Activity; the prov:used domain would incorrectly force ExecutionAuthorization ⊑ prov:Activity."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#authorizesRun> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "authorizes run"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextDataset
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextDataset> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextDataset> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#SharedEvaluationContext> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The dcat:Dataset the evaluation context is defined over. Functional. Not declared a subproperty of it6:trainedOn because an evaluation-context dataset is an evaluation dataset, not necessarily a training dataset."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextDataset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "context dataset"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextFlow
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextFlow> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextFlow> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextFlow> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#SharedEvaluationContext> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextFlow> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://data.europa.eu/it6/Flow> .
<http://data.europa.eu/it6/Flow> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextFlow> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The it6:Flow (pipeline / reproducibility artefact) referenced by the evaluation context. Functional. Not declared a subproperty of it6:hasFlow because the evaluation context is not itself a run."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextFlow> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "context flow"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextTask
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextTask> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextTask> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://data.europa.eu/it6/hasTask> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextTask> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextTask> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#SharedEvaluationContext> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextTask> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://data.europa.eu/it6/Task> .
<http://data.europa.eu/it6/Task> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextTask> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The it6:Task the evaluation context is defined over. Functional."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#contextTask> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "context task"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#deploysModel
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#deploysModel> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#deploysModel> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#deploysModel> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#deploysModel> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#ModelDeployment> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#deploysModel> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://data.europa.eu/it6/MachineLearningModel> .
<http://data.europa.eu/it6/MachineLearningModel> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#deploysModel> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a deployment to the model it serves. Functional: one deployment serves one model. Asymmetric: a deployment and its model are distinct individuals."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#deploysModel> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "deploys model"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#derivedFromRun
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#derivedFromRun> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#derivedFromRun> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasGeneratedBy> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#derivedFromRun> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#derivedFromRun> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#derivedFromRun> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#DerivedArtifact> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#derivedFromRun> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://data.europa.eu/it6/Run> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#derivedFromRun> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a derived artifact to the run that produced it. Functional: each derived artifact has exactly one originating run. Asymmetric: an artifact and its generating run are distinct."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#derivedFromRun> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "derived from run"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#evidenceOf
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#evidenceOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#evidenceOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#evidenceOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#evidenceOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#AuditEvidence> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#evidenceOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#evidenceOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links audit evidence to the activity it attests. Functional. Asymmetric: audit evidence is distinct from the activity it records. Deliberately NOT declared a subproperty of prov:hadActivity: that property is used on reified influence/generation/usage objects, not on entities — an AuditEvidence is a prov:Entity that is ABOUT an activity, which PROV-O does not provide a direct property for."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#evidenceOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "evidence of"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#exposedAs
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#exposedAs> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#exposedAs> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#ModelDeployment> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#exposedAs> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#DataService> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#DataService> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#exposedAs> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a deployment to the DCAT data service(s) that expose it. Non-functional: one deployment may expose multiple endpoints (e.g., a REST service plus a gRPC service, or regional load-balanced endpoints). Each service's I/O contract can differ (see daimo:hasIOContract, also non-functional)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#exposedAs> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "exposed as"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#grantedTo
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#grantedTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#grantedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/odrl/2/assignee> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#grantedTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#grantedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#ExecutionAuthorization> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#grantedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent> .
<http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#grantedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an authorization to the grantee agent. Functional. Specialises odrl:assignee (the ODRL party receiving an agreement's terms). Deliberately NOT aligned to prov:qualifiedAssociation: that property points to a reified prov:Association object, not to the agent itself; using it here would incorrectly type every grantee Agent as a prov:Association."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#grantedTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "granted to"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasAuditEvidence
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasAuditEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasAuditEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#evidenceOf> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasAuditEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasAuditEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#AuditEvidence> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasAuditEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of daimo:evidenceOf: from an activity, retrieve every audit-evidence record attesting it. Non-functional (multiple auditors can independently attest the same activity)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasAuditEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has audit evidence"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasDeployment
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasDeployment> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasDeployment> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#deploysModel> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasDeployment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://data.europa.eu/it6/MachineLearningModel> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasDeployment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#ModelDeployment> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasDeployment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of daimo:deploysModel: from a model, retrieve every deployment that serves it. Non-functional (a model can have multiple deployments across contexts)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasDeployment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has deployment"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasDerivedArtifact
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasDerivedArtifact> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasDerivedArtifact> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#derivedFromRun> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasDerivedArtifact> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://data.europa.eu/it6/Run> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasDerivedArtifact> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#DerivedArtifact> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasDerivedArtifact> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of daimo:derivedFromRun: from a run, retrieve every derived artifact it produced. Non-functional (a run may produce multiple governed outputs)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasDerivedArtifact> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has derived artifact"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasIOContract
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasIOContract> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasIOContract> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#ModelDeployment> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasIOContract> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#IOContract> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasIOContract> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a deployment to its invocation contract(s). Non-functional: a deployment exposing multiple services (see daimo:exposedAs) may carry a distinct IOContract per protocol (e.g., JSON+OAuth2 for REST and protobuf+mTLS for gRPC)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasIOContract> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has I/O contract"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOfferPolicy
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOfferPolicy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOfferPolicy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/odrl/2/hasPolicy> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOfferPolicy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOfferPolicy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#AIAssetOffering> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOfferPolicy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/odrl/2/Offer> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/odrl/2/Offer> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOfferPolicy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an offering to the ODRL offer policy that governs the offered model. Functional: each offering carries exactly one canonical offer policy."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOfferPolicy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has offer policy"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOffering
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOffering> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOffering> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/isPrimaryTopicOf> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOffering> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offersModel> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOffering> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://data.europa.eu/it6/MachineLearningModel> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOffering> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#AIAssetOffering> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOffering> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Inverse of daimo:offersModel: from a model, retrieve every catalog offering that registers it. Non-functional (the same model may be offered by different providers in different catalogs). Declared rdfs:subPropertyOf foaf:isPrimaryTopicOf for symmetry with daimo:offersModel ⊑ foaf:primaryTopic."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasOffering> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has offering"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasRole
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#ParticipantRole> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an agent to a dataspace role. Non-functional: agents may hold multiple roles."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#hasRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has role"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#inParticipantContext
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#inParticipantContext> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#inParticipantContext> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#inParticipantContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#ParticipantRole> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#inParticipantContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/edc/v0.0.1/ns/ParticipantContext> .
<https://w3id.org/edc/v0.0.1/ns/ParticipantContext> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#inParticipantContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Scopes a role assignment to a specific EDC participant context. Functional: a role instance is held within exactly one context."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#inParticipantContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "in participant context"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#inputSchema
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#inputSchema> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#inputSchema> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#inputSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#IOContract> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#inputSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Resource> .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Resource> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#inputSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Optional link to a resource describing the input payload schema (JSON Schema, SHACL shape, etc.)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#inputSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "input schema"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#integrityHash
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#integrityHash> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#integrityHash> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#integrityHash> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#AuditEvidence> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#integrityHash> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://spdx.org/rdf/terms#Checksum> .
<http://spdx.org/rdf/terms#Checksum> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#integrityHash> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links audit evidence to an spdx:Checksum that bundles the algorithm (spdx:algorithm) and the digest value (spdx:checksumValue). Functional: exactly one canonical checksum per evidence record. A plain-string digest without its algorithm cannot be verified, so a structured spdx:Checksum is required rather than an xsd:string."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#integrityHash> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "integrity hash"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offeredBy
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offeredBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offeredBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offeredBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#AIAssetOffering> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offeredBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offeredBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an offering to the agent that authored the offered AI model (i.e., the model provider). Functional: each offering has exactly one offering agent. Deliberately NOT declared rdfs:subPropertyOf dct:publisher: on a dcat:CatalogRecord, dct:publisher denotes the catalog maintainer (the platform registering the record), not the author of the asset being registered. Conflating them would entail that the catalog-time publisher is the model creator — semantically wrong in a real dataspace where e.g. INESData publishes records authored by UPM."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offeredBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "offered by"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offersModel
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offersModel> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offersModel> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/primaryTopic> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offersModel> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offersModel> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AsymmetricProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offersModel> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#AIAssetOffering> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offersModel> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://data.europa.eu/it6/MachineLearningModel> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offersModel> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a catalog-record offering to the AI model it registers. Functional: one offering registers exactly one model. Asymmetric: an offering is distinct from the model it offers."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#offersModel> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "offers model"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#onInfrastructure
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#onInfrastructure> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#onInfrastructure> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#onInfrastructure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#ModelDeployment> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#onInfrastructure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://data.europa.eu/it6/ComputerInfrastructure> .
<http://data.europa.eu/it6/ComputerInfrastructure> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#onInfrastructure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a deployment to the MLDCAT-AP computer infrastructure running it. Functional: one deployment runs on one canonical infrastructure instance (redundancy is modelled as multiple deployments)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#onInfrastructure> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "on infrastructure"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#outputSchema
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#outputSchema> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#outputSchema> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#outputSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#IOContract> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#outputSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Resource> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#outputSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Optional link to a resource describing the output payload schema."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#outputSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "output schema"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#records
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#records> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#records> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#CrossParticipantProvenanceRecord> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#records> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#records> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a cross-participant provenance bundle to each prov:Activity that forms part of the audit-ready narrative."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#records> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "records"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#signedBy
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#signedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#signedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#signedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#AuditEvidence> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#signedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#signedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Functional: one signer per evidence record."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#signedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "signed by"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#spansParticipantContext
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#spansParticipantContext> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#spansParticipantContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#CrossParticipantProvenanceRecord> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#spansParticipantContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/edc/v0.0.1/ns/ParticipantContext> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#spansParticipantContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a cross-participant provenance bundle to each participant context whose activities or entities it records. A record must span at least two contexts (enforced by SHACL)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#spansParticipantContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "spans participant context"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#underAuthorization
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#underAuthorization> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#underAuthorization> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#underAuthorization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#DerivedArtifact> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#underAuthorization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#ExecutionAuthorization> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#underAuthorization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a derived artifact to the authorisation under which it was produced. Functional."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#underAuthorization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "under authorization"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#usesEvaluationContext
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#usesEvaluationContext> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#usesEvaluationContext> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#usesEvaluationContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://data.europa.eu/it6/Evaluation> .
<http://data.europa.eu/it6/Evaluation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#usesEvaluationContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#SharedEvaluationContext> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#usesEvaluationContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links an it6:Evaluation to the shared evaluation context under which its results are comparable to other evaluations. Functional."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#usesEvaluationContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "uses evaluation context"@en .
