<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#datasetVersion> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#datasetVersion> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#datasetVersion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#SharedEvaluationContext> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#datasetVersion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#datasetVersion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Literal version identifier of the evaluation dataset used by the context. Deliberately not aligned to dct:hasVersion because dct:hasVersion relates a resource to another version resource, whereas DAIMO records the dataset-version token as a literal for reproducible benchmarking."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#datasetVersion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "dataset version"@en .
# 
