<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#expiresAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#ExecutionAuthorization> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#expiresAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#expiresAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Expiry timestamp of the execution authorisation."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#expiresAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "expires at"@en .
