<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#outputFormat> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "IANA media type of the produced output payload (e.g. \"application/geo+json\")."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#outputFormat> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "output format"@en .
