# https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#randomSeed
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#randomSeed> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#randomSeed> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#FunctionalProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#randomSeed> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#SharedEvaluationContext> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#randomSeed> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer> .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#randomSeed> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Random seed fixing stochastic components of the protocol, required for reproducibility."@en .
