_:genid3 <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Asserts that the nine top-level DAIMO-native kinds are pairwise disjoint. ParticipantRole subclasses are deliberately excluded so that a single agent may simultaneously hold several roles (e.g., a research group acting as both Evaluator and Model Provider)."@en .
